## type [HttpResponse](https://github.com/jdfalk/gcommon/blob/main/gcommon/sdks/go/v1/web/http_response.pb.go#L34-L70)

\* HttpResponse represents an HTTP response from web services. Captures all
essential HTTP response information including status, headers, body, and
metadata for service mesh and proxy use cases.
